name: Commutiny-The Youth Collective
briefDescription: We nurture 5th Spaces for youth development since 2008. We believe •	We need 5th Spaces  - spaces that equip young people to take care of their self development, make decisions and take action that is beneficial to themselves and their surroundings.•	We need to support all those who influence the present and future of youth to push limits – of their own visions and of society – to see the value of 5th Spaces and legitimize it.We are a collective of like-minded professionals from diverse fields. We wish to see a world that offers every young person opportunities to realize her/his potential as individuals, and as stakeholders in the larger society. Our key supporters are DKA -Austria, India Development Services – USA,  Sir Ratan Tata
